INSTALLING MEDUSA

Directory layout:
- `src/`: all C/C++ source and header files
- `build/obj/`: object files produced by `make`
- repository root: executables, documentation, scripts, and generated output dirs

Build:
- `make all`

Clean binaries and object files:
- `make clean`

Generate example graphics (PDF):
- `./generate_graphics.sh`
- or `./generate_graphics.sh <output_dir>`


Programs were written by Christian Henriksen, David Farris, and Kuan Ju
Liu at Cornell University in Summer 1998.
